channel.title: Rune474 - V2 - Easier to use! Loads more features!
channel.description:
[CENTER][SIZE="6"]Rune474 V2[/SIZE]
Hey guys! I think it's time I coded my V2 base, including more features than the last server. I also made this base more Noob-friendly by refactoring the java files to the 317 style java files. Client.java, player.java etc.. I had to rush this server.. so here I will list all the updates I added:
Loads item list. 13k+ (from 508 servers) Loads NPC+NPC Autospawn list. Loads item names, especially for the attack interface. "Abyssal Whip" etc.. Different attack styles(cheapest way, you can edit it) Adds skill xp depending on which attack style(cheap way) sendMessage working(can change colour of it too) setConfig2 working(loads spec bar) credits to richard1992 :) Npcs fight back. Fighting animations, range too. Weapon timers base. Emotes glitch has been fixed. Skillcape emotes added. ::godswords, ::skillcapes, ::skillcapest, ::hoods Added combat! Added a base to find configs such as trade, duel arena and prayer etc.. FIXED EQUIPMENT BUG! NOW EQUIPMENT SCREEN SHOWS ARMOUR.. FINALLY? Added levelling. Added run energy, + running. BTW: CHANGE playerEnergy to 100, otherwise you can't run! Found sendCoords frame. credits to mage_owner-- can be used to create ground items, create projectiles etc. AND ALOT MORE! Here are some pics:
[IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/sbhwd0.png[/img] [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/eg4pj9.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/e66dl1.png[/img] [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/2h6bvxe.png[/img] [/CENTER]
This is a base made only for the non-expert coders, I have made it easy to use! All you do is download the 474 package, extract it, run the server and then run the client! no cache shit required! cache is located in the client.
[B][U][SIZE="5"]BTW: YOU HAVE TO RUN THE SERVER BEFORE RUNNING THE CLIENT![/SIZE][/U][/B]
/** * If the links are down; PM me I will be more than happy to upload! * @author Vigan. */ Download Links: [url=http://www.megaupload.com/?d=DHMHO7O9]http://www.megaupload.com/?d=DHMHO7O9[/url] http://www.mediafire.com/?sharekey=8d4173ac2a871f680f83d91f6dff7c38c86844f97782937b5be6ba49b5870170 //MORE DOWNLOAD LINKS COMING SOON.
Comes with server + client. WARNING: Using another client will not show equipment on equipment screen, because its kinda refactored + editted. Thanks for viewing, and probably downloading, Vigan20.
